    tex_list.append(word)

               max_words=200,
               contour_width=3,
               contour_color='steelblue', 
               font_path=path)
In [ ]:
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(30,30))

for t in range(lda.num_topics):
  plt.subplot(5,4,t+1)
  x = dict(lda.show_topic(t,200))    # 주제별 200개의 단어 보기
  im = wc.generate_from_frequencies(x)
  plt.imshow(im)
  plt.axis("off")
  plt.title("Topic #" + str(t))

plt.savefig('LDA_wordcloud.png', dpi=300, bbox_inches='tight')
plt.show()
plt.close(fig)

               max_words=2000,
               contour_width=3,
               contour_color='steelblue', 
               font_path=path)

plt.figure(figsize=(30,30))
for t in range(lda.num_topics):
  plt.subplot(5,4,t+1)
  x = dict(lda.show_topic(t,200))
  im = wc.generate_from_frequencies(x)
  plt.imshow(im)
  plt.axis("off")
  plt.title("Topic #" + str(t))

plt.savefig('LDA_wordcloud.png', bbox_inches='tight')
